    "title": "New Event: Launch of SUIIT Library Software",
    "content": "<div class=\"container my-5\">\n  <div\n    class=\"p-5\"\n    style=\"\n      background-color: #f8f9fa;\n      border-radius: 15px;\n      box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    \"\n  >\n    <!-- Logo -->\n    <div class=\"text-center mb-4\">\n      <img\n        src=\"https://i0.wp.com/suiit.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/logo-e1691752288216.png?w=300&ssl=1\"\n        alt=\"SUIIT Logo\"\n        style=\"width: 120px; height: auto;\"\n      />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Event Title -->\n    <h1\n      class=\"text-center mb-4\"\n      style=\"color: #046655; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\"\n    >\n      <i class=\"bi bi-megaphone-fill me-2\"></i>Launch of SUIIT Library Software\n    </h1>\n    <hr style=\"border-top: 3px solid #046655; width: 60%; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n\n    <!-- Event Description -->\n    <p\n      class=\"mt-4\"\n      style=\"color: #333; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6;\"\n    >\n      <strong>Dear Students and Faculty,</strong> <br />\n      We are excited to introduce the <strong>SUIIT Library Software</strong>,\n      our cutting-edge platform designed to revolutionize library management at\n      SUIIT. Access it now at:\n      <a\n        href=\"https://library.suiit.ac.in\"\n        target=\"_blank\"\n        style=\"color: #046655; text-decoration: underline;\"\n      >\n        library.suiit.ac.in\n      </a>\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Key Features Section -->\n    <div\n      class=\"mt-4 p-3\"\n      style=\"\n        background-color: #fff;\n        border-radius: 10px;\n        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n      \"\n    >\n      <h4 style=\"color: #046655; font-weight: bold;\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-star-fill me-2\" style=\"color: #ffcc00;\"></i>Key\n        Features\n      </h4>\n      <ul\n        class=\"list-group mt-3\"\n        style=\"\n          font-size: 1rem;\n          font-weight: 500;\n          color: #333;\n          line-height: 1.6;\n        \"\n      >\n        <li\n          class=\"list-group-item\"\n          style=\"border: none; background-color: transparent;\"\n        >\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.3rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          Effortless book search and catalog browsing\n        </li>\n        <li\n          class=\"list-group-item\"\n          style=\"border: none; background-color: transparent;\"\n        >\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.3rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          Online book reservation and issuance\n        </li>\n        <li\n          class=\"list-group-item\"\n          style=\"border: none; background-color: transparent;\"\n        >\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.3rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          User-friendly dashboard for students and faculty\n        </li>\n        <li\n          class=\"list-group-item\"\n          style=\"border: none; background-color: transparent;\"\n        >\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.3rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          Real-time updates and notifications\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Event Details -->\n    <div class=\"mt-4\">\n      <h4 style=\"color: #046655; font-weight: bold;\">\n        <i class=\"bi bi-calendar2-event-fill me-2\"></i>Event Details\n      </h4>\n      <div\n        class=\"d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-3\"\n        style=\"font-size: 1rem; color: #333;\"\n      >\n        <div>\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-calendar2-date-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.2rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          <strong>Date:</strong> January 20, 2025\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-clock-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.2rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          <strong>Time:</strong> 11:00 AM\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <i\n            class=\"bi bi-geo-alt-fill me-2\"\n            style=\"color: #046655; font-size: 1.2rem;\"\n          ></i>\n          <strong>Venue:</strong> SUIIT Auditorium\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Invitation -->\n    <p\n      class=\"mt-4\"\n      style=\"color: #333; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic;\"\n    >\n      Join us for a live demonstration and walkthrough of the platform's\n      features, followed by refreshments.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Action Button -->\n    <div class=\"text-center mt-4\">\n      <a\n        href=\"https://library.suiit.ac.in\"\n        target=\"_blank\"\n        class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\"\n        style=\"\n          background-color: #046655;\n          border: none;\n          font-size: 1.2rem;\n          font-weight: bold;\n          text-transform: uppercase;\n        \"\n      >\n        <i class=\"bi bi-link-45deg me-2\"></i>Explore Library.suiit.ac.in\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n",
